Marketing Systems of America Incsaid it has retained Richter, Cohen and Co to assist in effortsto redirect its business through merger or acquisition.    The company said as consideration for services to berenedered, it has agreed to grant Richter five-year warrants tobuy 231,000 common shares at 32 cts each, exercisable startingin March 1988, and a negotiated fee on completion of anytransaction.  It said it has the right to cancel the warrantsafter one year if no transaction has been completed. Reuter&#3;